Set Shell zsh
Set TypingSpeed 80ms

Set FontSize 32
Set Width 2200
Set Height 800

Hide

Type "source ~/.zshrc" Enter
Type "nvim ./tests/fixtures/empty-section.txt" Enter

Show

Sleep 500ms

Type "[c" Sleep 500ms
Type "ct" Sleep 500ms

Sleep 1s

Type "[c" Sleep 500ms
Type "ct" Sleep 500ms

Sleep 3s
